Method 1:
Preorder Traversal with remaining sum-
if root null: return false
if leaf node: return remaining==root->val
remaining-=root->value
return preorder(left side)||preorder(right side)

Method 2:
Preorder Traversal with Current sum-
if root null : return false;
current sum+=root->value
if leaf node: return curSum==TargetSum
return preorder(left side)||preorder(right side)
